Introduction

Park Jiwon is a South Korean singer-songwriter, dancer, and composer under ASND. She was the main vocalist of the girl group fromis_9.

Jiwon was first known as a JYP Trainee who competed in the survival show Sixteen, placing 13th in the final rankings. Although she didn't make it, she continued to pursue her dreams. Eventually, Jiwon competed in the show "Idol School" where she ranked 6th with 63,816 votes, earning her a spot in the group fromis_9.

Jiwon debuted as a member of fromis_9 on January 24, 2018, with the mini album To. Heart.
